472
00:21:23.979 --> 00:21:25.165
All right.

473
00:21:25.189 --> 00:21:27.375
Yeah. I know who to ask where.

474
00:21:27.399 --> 00:21:28.960
- I can get you the info.
- Okay.

475
00:21:28.984 --> 00:21:31.004
